The full moon gazes down at me.[l] Staring at it absentmindedly, I take a swig of beer. The bitterness and smoothness, I’ve lost count how many times I've done this, hits my stomach and makes me feel alive.[l][r]
Yes, I am alive. Both Yuu and I are alive.[l][r]
...But can you really call this living?[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

