With a crunch, I crush the empty can in my hand.[l][r]
[r]Why is everything so painful? Why does my heart ache so much?[l][r]
[r]Day after day, my heart keeps wearing out. I should be happy, and yet my heart screams like a child.[l][r]

[_tb_end_text]

