[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
This is a world where Yuu exists. No matter how much I cry, Yuu will hold me tight. I should be happy about that. I should be happy that we can be together.[l][r]

[r]Then why…?[l][r]
Tears overflow again. I wipe them away and open another beer can.[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

