There were already four cans rolling on the floor.[l][r]
I drink. I savor it. But I can’t taste anything. It's not as bitter as before, and the coldness doesn't hit my stomach. Why?[l][r]
[r]Damn it, damn it, damn it! Why is this happening!![l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

