[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
Deep down, I know the truth.[l][r]

[r]Oh, it's you again. Shut up, leave me alone.[l][r]

[r]You are alone. We’ve become one in the same.[l][r]

[r]Don’t talk. Get out of my head.[l][r]

[r]I can't do that.[r]
I told you, we are "Chi." Everything you think about, everything you turn away from, everything you desire.[l][r]
I know all of it.[l][r]
[r]"Shut up!"[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

[cm  ]
[tb_start_text mode=3 ]
I yelped impulsively. There was no answer.[l][r]
I'm out of breath. I'm sweating. My whole body is wrapped in discomfort. To forget it, I down another beer in one gulp.[l][r]

[r]Damn it, more, it's too lukewarm, I don’t feel anything, damn, damn, damn!![l][r]
[r]"Damn…"[l][r]
[r]Tears overflow from my cheeks.[r]
Why, why. I don’t understand.[l][r]

[cm]I don’t understand. No matter how much I try to know, to understand, I can't.[l][r]
[r]I don’t get it… no matter how much I think about it, there’s no answer…[l][r]
I don’t want to think about it anymore…[l][r]
[_tb_end_text]

